node.title: Can’t take my eyes off you

node.text:
A fighter ready to take up all challenges that life throws his way with such dignity and grace and surviving through them all so graciously 🙏🏼 I’m in complete awe of  Mr Albert , a thorough gentleman indeed and I admire and respect his will power , positivity , his zeal zest and enthusiasm for living his life , so passionately - “ is jasbe ko mera salaam “ . 🙏🏼🕊🦋
I’m inspired and deeply moved and I aspire to grow up as high spirited as him❤️
I can’t help but repost this on my page because it’s so beautiful and we need to see more such videos , share it with your families , your parents , your friends and all your loved ones ❤️#repost #albert #99 #beautiful  #fighter #survivor #respect #inspired #loveandlight
